name: Work 00001 mountain landscape digital impressionist
description: A mountain landscape for Earth Day 2021, and also for #WorldArtDay2021. I hope that crypto art NFTs bring more beauty into the world. This work (00001) is the first I published on my journey into digital art starting around 2011, falling in love with possibilities of simulated media. The reference photograph was taken with an iPhone of all things. A lot of virtual watercolor, layering, hand painting and filters (including Filter Forge) went into this. 2592x1936, many details in image metadata.
